--- /dev/null
+++ b/docs/document/content/concepts/distsql/syntax/rql/rql-single-table.cn.md
@@ -0,0 +1,33 @@
++++
+title = "单表"
+weight = 7
++++
+
+## 定义
+
+```sql
+SHOW SINGLE TABLE (tableRule | RULES) [FROM schemaName]
+
+tableRule:
+    RULE tableName
+```
+
+## 说明
+
+| 列            | 说明          |
+| ------------- | ------------ |
+| table_name    | 单表名称      |
+| resource_name | 数据源名称    |
+
+## 示例
+
+```sql
+mysql> show single table rules;
++--------------+---------------+
+| table_name   | resource_name |
++--------------+---------------+
+| t_single_0   | ds_0          |
+| t_single_1   | ds_1          |
++--------------+---------------+
+2 rows in set (0.02 sec)
+```
